---
resource_links: 
  - title : "Visit Myrkwood on Instagram"
    icon: "instagram"
    url: "https://www.instagram.com/myrkwood_mushrooms/"
    external: true
  - title : "Download our informational flier"
    icon: "download"
    url: "/documents/myrkwood_mushrooms_info_sheet.png"
partners:
  - name: "Raleigh City Farm"
    image: 'raleighcityfarm.png'
    url: "https://raleighcityfarm.org/"  
  - name: "Leaf & Limb"
    image: "leaflimb.svg"
    url: "https://www.leaflimb.com/"
  - name: "Bull City Gardens"
    image: 'bullcitygardens.png'
    url: "http://bullcitygardens.com/"
prices:
  - title: "Old Faithful"
    price: "$200"
    description:
      '3 ✕ 6 ft. mushroom bed constructed from high quality, naturally rot-resistant cedar planks. Used for the cultivation of oyster mushrooms, wine caps, or wood blewits. Fruits in as little as 6 weeks.'
  - title: "Myrkwood Logs"
    price: "$50/log"
    description:
      "3 - 4 ft. hand cut and selected local hardwood logs pre-drilled and inoculated with oyster or shiitake spawn. Fruits for 2-4 years."
  - title: "Indoor fruiting block"
    price: "$50 each"
    description:
      "5 lb. 'spray and grow' block ready to fruit for oyster, lion's mane, shiitake, or reishi mushrooms."
  - title: "Oyster mushroom pots"
    price: "$20 each"
    description:
      "Perfect for small patios and apartments, your choice of oyster mushrooms ready to fruit in containers."
  - title: "Custom projects"
    price: ""
    description:
      "Specialty mushroom species, trees, garden plants, medicinal plants design and installation."
  - title: "Mycology research and education"
    price: ""
    description:
      "Scientific consulting, laboratory work, and product development. If you have an idea that relates to plants and fungi please <a class='underline' href='#contact'>contact us</a> to design and execute a project or educational event."
sidePadding: px-1
---
<section
  class="min-h-screen bg-accent-1 pt-5 pb-6 px-0 relative"
  id="splash">
  <div
    class="max-w-screen-md w-full mx-auto relative z-10 px-1">
    <h1
      class="sr-only">{{site.title}}
    </h1>
    <div>
      <img
        alt="Myrkwood Mushrooms logo showing mushrooms and oak tree"
        class="animate-fade-in w-full max-w-screen-sm mx-auto xl:max-w-screen-md min-h-custom-228 md:min-h-custom-360 xl:min-h-custom-564"
        height="150"
        src="images/logo_CW.svg"
        width="200" />
    </div>
    <p
      class="font-display py-4 text-2xl text-center sm:text-2xl">Backyard mushroom gardens in the Triangle, NC
    </p>
    <p
      class="font-display p-0 text-center uppercase">Raleigh | Durham | Cary
    </p>
    <a
      class="w-4 animate-spring pt-5 block mx-auto"
      href="#about">
      <img
        alt="Down arrow"
        src="images/down.svg" />
    </a>
  </div>
  {% comment %}
    <img
        class="absolute top-0 w-full background hidden"
        src="images/mushrooms.jpg" />
    {% endcomment %}
</section>
<section
  class="min-h-screen bg-light {{sidePadding}} pt-7"
  id="about">
  <div
    class="container flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:items-center">
    <div
      class="flex-1 pb-2">
      {% render 'h2', text:"Welcome to Myrkwood."%}
      <p>
        Myrkwood (Old Norse, "dark wood" or "black forest”) is the wild, primitive forest of ancient Europe. In
                the Norse tradition, "crossing the Black Forest" came to signify penetrating the barriers between one
                world and another. In this sense, Myrkwood
                Mushrooms aims to connect you with the joy and benefits of the natural world, right in your
                own backyard.
      </p>
      <p>Fungi are essential for soil health, the growth of plants, and for the decomposition of
                wood and other organic matter. Not only are fungi ecological workhorses, but their fruits, mushrooms,
                are fun and easy to grow, providing delicious food and beneficial medicines.
      </p>
      <p>We can help you install and cultivate your very own sustainable mushroom garden. From simple mushroom
                logs and beds to large scale permaculture projects, our 10+ years of experience will yield you results
                time and time again.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="flex-1 py-4 lg:pl-5">
      {% picture 'images/mushrooms.jpg' 'alt text' 'shadow rounded-sm'%}
    </div>
  </div>
  <div
    class="container flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:items-center">
    <div
      class="flex-1 lg:order-2">
      {% render 'h3', text: "Meet the mushroom guru." %}
      <p
        class="lg:mb-4">
        Charlie, owner and operator of Myrkwood Mushrooms, holds a doctorate in Plant & Microbial Biology from
                NC State University (2020). An ethnobotanist
                by training, Charlie is an expert in the traditional usage of medicinal plants and fungi by cultures
                throughout the world. He has nearly 10 years of horticulture and mushroom growing experience.
      </p>
      {% render 'in-page-link', url: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/charles-wagner-32259a18b/' , title: "Connect on LinkedIn", icon: 'external-link', external: true %}
      {% render 'in-page-link', url: "https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Charles-Wagner" , title: "Learn about Charlie's research", icon: 'external-link', external: true %}
    </div>
    <div
      class="flex-1 py-4 lg:pr-5 lg:order-1">
      {% picture'images/charlie.jpg' 'Charlie smiling and holding a mushroom in front of some trees' 'shadow rounded-sm' %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section
  class="min-h-screen {{sidePadding}} pt-4 lg:pt-6 pb-6"
  id="how-it-works">
  <div
    class="container flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:items-center">
    <div
      class="flex-1 lg:px-4">
      {% render 'h2', text: "How it works"%}
      <ol
        class="list-decimal pl-2 text-l">
        <li>Schedule a visit or virtual consultation to assess the property, determine what you want to grow, and develop
                    a plan for the garden.
        </li>
        <li>Choose an installation date to build and inoculate the garden.
        </li>
        <li>Opt for periodic maintenance. We keep an open door for you to join in for a hands-on experience
                    anytime you like.
        </li>
        <li>When it comes time to harvest, receive mentorship for proper use of your mushrooms.
        </li>
      </ol>
      {% render 'in-page-link', title: 'Download instructions for caring for your mushrooms', url: '/documents/myrkwood_mushrooms_care_sheet.pdf', icon: 'download', external: false %}
    </div>
    <div
      class="flex-1 py-4 lg:pl-5 flex flex-col">
      <div
        class="p-2"
        style="max-width:375px">
        {% picture'images/beds.jpg' 'alt text' 'shadow rounded-sm' '350px' %}
      </div>
      <div
        class="p-2 justify-self-end self-end"
        style="max-width: 450px">
        {% picture'images/logs.jpg' 'alt text' 'shadow rounded-sm' '450px'%}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div
    class="container flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:items-center">
    <div
      class="flex-1 lg:px-4">
      {% render 'h3', text: "Plans and prices"%}
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-1 grid-rows-none md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
        {% for service in prices %}
          {% render 'price-card', title: service.title, price: service.price, description: service.description %}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  {% comment %}
    <div
        class="container flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:items-center">
        <div
            class="flex-1 lg:px-4">
            {% render 'h3', text: "Mycology Research and Education"%}
            <p>
                Scientific consulting, laboratory work, and product development. If you have an idea that relates to plants and fungi please contact us to design and execute a project or educational event.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    {% endcomment %}
</section>
<section
  class="min-h-screen  {{sidePadding}} pt-4 pb-6 lg:py-6"
  id="contact">
  <div
    class="container max-w-screen-md mb-6 flex flex-col
      justify-center items-center">
    {% render 'h2', text: "Get in touch", classes: "text-center" %}
    {% render 'contact-form'%}
  </div>
  <div
    class="container max-w-screen-md mb-6 flex flex-col
      justify-center items-center">
    {% render 'h3', text: "Join our email list", classes: "text-center" %}
    <p>Sign up to find out when we have mushrooms for sale and other Myrkwood news. </p>
    {% render 'email-form'%}
  </div>
  {% for resource in resource_links %}
    {% render 'resource-link', url: resource.url, title: resource.title, icon: resource.icon, external: resource.external %}
  {% endfor %}
</section>
<section class="{{sidePadding}} pb-4">
  {% render 'h2', text: "Our partners", classes: "text-center" %}
  <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-center items-center">
  {% for partner in partners %}
    <a class="px-4 h-custom-228 flex items-center" aria-label={{partner.name}} href={{partner.url}}>
      <img
        class="transition-all transform hover:scale-125"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer"
        alt="Logo for {{partner.name}}"
        src="images/{{partner.image}}"
        width="200" />
    </a>
  {% endfor%}
  </div>  
</section>
